@node req "What you need..."
You don't have to be rich or to make Bill Gates richer.

The minimum is...

An Amiga (even an A500+ will do fine)
A monitor (well, a resolution of 1x1 is just an advice)
A hard disk, a floppy disk, a Zip disk, whatever disk.
A couple of eyes (Those you have on your head not on your screen, put on your glasses if they're deficient)

But I recommend...

An Amiga 1200 (Kick 3.1 installed, not only to have the latest but to have better gfx results)
A Good hard disk (the more GBytes the better)
2 or 4 Mbytes of FAST (the more the merrier)
A MC68020 or more

That's it
@endnode

@node inst "Installation"
You should proceed in two steps

1° Set the 16 colors @{" palette " link "pal"},
2° Replace your icons using SwazInfo, Iconian or anything else...
3° Remap the MWB icons that look trashed and contact the @{"author" link "author"} to ask him if he can do something for these icons.
@endnode

